SpecEE_cloud — Modified derivative of SpecEE
============================================

This directory contains code derived from the SpecEE project:

  Original repository: https://github.com/infinigence/SpecEE
  Paper: "SpecEE: Accelerating Large Language Model Inference with Speculative Early Exiting"
  Authors: Jiaming Xu, Jiayi Pan, Yongkang Zhou, Siming Chen, Jinhao Li,
           Yaoxiu Lian, Junyi Wu, Guohao Dai
  Copyright 2024 OpenBMB
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

Modifications by the EarlyExitLLM team (ECE1513 Final Project):
  - Added Apple MPS (Metal) device support for macOS inference
  - Modified device selection logic (CUDA -> MPS -> CPU fallback)
  - Integrated custom MLP predictor loading (state_dict format)
